These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pepper, apple, kale, peach, strawberry, cherry, carrot
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person eating pepper is between the person eating peach and the person eating carrot##2
 2. the person eating apple is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 9. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
10. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Food   | peach | pepper | carrot | apple    | kale | strawberry   | cherry    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: chess, backgammon, billiard, snooker, bridge, canasta, whist
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing canasta and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Game          | bridge | billiard | canasta | backgammon | whist | chess      | snooker  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

