.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, cooking, traveling, collecting, rock-climbing, photography, card-games
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | card-games | rock-climbing | camping | cooking   | collecting | traveling | photography |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

