.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, thai, polish, german, turkish, argentine, indonesian
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the thai##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the indonesian and the dutch##2
4. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the dutch##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the german##1
9. the turkish is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Nationality   | german      | turkish | dutch | polish | indonesian      | thai      | argentine |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

