4. the paramedic is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the futuristic house##1
6. the futuristic house is between the craftsman house and the firefighter##2
7. the craftsman house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | scientist | firefighter | project-manager | videographer | paramedic | pilot     | writer |
| House   | art-deco   | tower    | futuristic    | craftsman      | townhouse  | colonial | palace |

