6. the project-manager is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the mechanic is on the right of the engineer##1
8. the software-developer is between the fan of rock and the project-manager##2
9. the fan of rock is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
